descr: "An assessment of the likely outcome(s) for a patient or other subject as well as the likelihood of each outcome."

fields.name: outcome
fields.descr: "One of the potential outcomes for the patient (e.g. remission, death,  a particular condition)."

fields.name: probabilityDecimal
fields.descr: "How likely is the outcome (in the specified timeframe)."

fields.name: probabilityRange
fields.descr: "How likely is the outcome (in the specified timeframe)."

fields.name: qualitativeRisk
fields.descr: "How likely is the outcome (in the specified timeframe), expressed as a qualitative value (e.g. low, medium, high)."

fields.name: relativeRisk
fields.descr: "Indicates the risk for this particular subject (with their specific characteristics) divided by the risk of the population in general.  (Numbers greater than 1 = higher risk than the population, numbers less than 1 = lower risk.)."

fields.name: whenPeriod
fields.descr: "Indicates the period of time or age range of the subject to which the specified probability applies."

fields.name: whenRange
fields.descr: "Indicates the period of time or age range of the subject to which the specified probability applies."

fields.name: rationale
fields.descr: "Additional information explaining the basis for the prediction."
